40:52.533 --> 40:54.369
THANK YOU.

40:57.122 --> 40:59.249
[ SIGHS ]

40:59.291 --> 41:02.460
WELL -- OH.

41:02.501 --> 41:04.587
HERE.

41:02.501 --> 41:04.587
THAT'S YOUR CUT.

41:04.629 --> 41:06.423
OH.

41:06.464 --> 41:09.426
AND, UH...

41:09.467 --> 41:13.596
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU

41:09.467 --> 41:13.596
YOUR EARBUD BACK.

41:13.638 --> 41:16.849
AND, LISTEN, YOU KNOW, I'LL TRY,

41:13.638 --> 41:16.849
BECAUSE SOPHIE SENT YOU,

41:16.891 --> 41:19.436
TRY  TO COMMUNICATE...

41:19.477 --> 41:21.396
BETTER.

41:21.438 --> 41:22.480
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

41:22.521 --> 41:25.317
THANK YOU.

41:25.358 --> 41:28.361
AND FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,

41:25.358 --> 41:28.361
SOPHIE WAS RIGHT.

41:28.403 --> 41:30.780
YOU GUYS  ARE  THE BEST

41:28.403 --> 41:30.780
I'VE EVER SEEN.

41:32.240 --> 41:33.825
I KNOW.

41:33.866 --> 41:35.785
[ Chuckling ]

41:33.866 --> 41:35.785
BUT NO ONE IN THE WORLD

41:35.827 --> 41:37.578
IS AS GOOD

41:35.827 --> 41:37.578
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

41:46.796 --> 41:48.423
ROUGH DAY?

41:48.465 --> 41:50.258
AH, WE GOT THROUGH IT OKAY.

41:50.300 --> 41:51.717
BARELY, FROM WHAT I HEARD.

41:51.759 --> 41:53.428
YEAH, WELL [SCOFFS]

41:53.470 --> 41:55.221
LISTEN, NATE, I SENT HER, SO --

41:55.263 --> 41:58.641
SO EVEN IF YOU DON'T TRUST HER,

41:55.263 --> 41:58.641
YOU SHOULD TRUST ME BY NOW.

41:58.683 --> 42:01.894
SHE WAS NEVER

41:58.683 --> 42:01.894
IN ANY REAL DANGER, SO...

42:01.936 --> 42:03.521
REALLY?

42:03.562 --> 42:05.523
SO WOULD YOU HAVE MADE

42:03.562 --> 42:05.523
THE SAME PLAY IF IT WERE ME?

42:05.564 --> 42:07.275
YEAH, PROBABLY.

42:07.317 --> 42:08.443
NO.

42:08.485 --> 42:10.736
NATE, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

42:10.778 --> 42:12.322
WHAT AM I DOING?

42:10.778 --> 42:12.322
I'M DOING MY JOB, SOPHIE!

42:12.364 --> 42:13.865
THE ONE THAT YOU

42:12.364 --> 42:13.865
TALKED ME BACK INTO DOING

42:13.906 --> 42:15.492
WHEN I WAS SITTING RIGHT HERE

42:13.906 --> 42:15.492
ON THIS COUCH!

42:15.533 --> 42:17.327
THE SAME ONE

42:15.533 --> 42:17.327
THAT YOU WALKED OUT ON.

42:17.369 --> 42:18.995
SO DON'T CALL ME

42:17.369 --> 42:18.995
FROM LONDON OR PARIS

42:19.037 --> 42:20.788
OR WHEREVER YOU ARE

42:19.037 --> 42:20.788
AND START TELLING ME,

42:20.830 --> 42:22.040
YOU KNOW, HOW TO RUN MY CREW!

42:22.081 --> 42:24.334
I'M SORRY,

42:22.081 --> 42:24.334
BUT IT'S JUST IF YOU --

42:24.376 --> 42:25.960
SOPHIE!

42:29.172 --> 42:31.257
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

42:33.926 --> 42:36.054
[ SIGHS ]
